{"tid":2388293,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"瑞信：2020年香港成人平均財富達逾400萬 僅次於瑞士","createTime":"2021-01-31T04:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T05:49:46.000Z","uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"822adcdd1ca4aba6fad9b63ab2fa483307ec09b2","tid":2388293,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T04:23:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2785615/港人財富榜%20-%20瑞信：2020年港成人平均財富達逾400萬%E3%80%80僅次於瑞士\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2785615%2F%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%A1%E5%AF%8C%E6%A6%9C%2520-%2520%E7%91%9E%E4%BF%A1%EF%BC%9A2020%E5%B9%B4%E6%B8%AF%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E8%B2%A1%E5%AF%8C%E9%81%94%E9%80%BE400%E8%90%AC%25E3%2580%2580%E5%83%85%E6%AC%A1%E6%96%BC%E7%91%9E%E5%A3%AB&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWqnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=46fe0026\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2785615/港人財富榜%20-%20瑞信：2020年港成人平均財富達逾400萬%E3%80%80僅次於瑞士</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2785000/2785615/201_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2785000%2F2785615%2F201_600.jpg&h=59123731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情衝擊全球經濟，或會影響個人財富收入。不過，最新研究調查顯示，2020年度中國及印度的家庭財富出現「疫市」增長，未來或會持續增加。<br />\n<br />\n瑞信發布《2020年全球財富報告》指出，受疫情拖累，今年1至3月份全球家庭財富減少17.5萬億美元（約135.6萬億港元）。經過3個月之後，由於全球股市反彈及房價回升，第二季度預測指出，全球家庭財富總額增長36.3萬億美元（約281.3萬億港元），相比去年年底略為上升。<br />\n<br />\n研究指出，亞太地區（包括中國和印度）家庭財富貢獻最高。在本年6月，其家庭財富總額高達167.2萬億美元（約1,294萬億港元），於上半年增長35,870億美元（約27萬億港元），佔全球42%。當中共有45,920位成人，淨資產超過5,000萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n香港方面，由於2019年期間股市飆升，導致成人人均家庭財富增長23,740美元（約18萬港元）。2020年的港成人人均財富，已達到518,810美元（約401萬港元），並僅次於瑞士。截至2019年底，全球共有5,190萬名百萬富翁，香港地區佔其中1%，淨資產超過5,000萬美元的成人則有2,910人。<br />\n<br />\n報告亦發現，今年全球的成人平均財富出現微降，每位成人平均財富從今年初的77,309美元（約599,160港元），降至平均76,984美元（約596,641港元）。當中瑞士、荷蘭、台北和香港出現增長，而挪威和英國跌幅最大。"},{"pid":"5d75c0daab160fee38f5e33f5d7ba6144138e0bc","tid":2388293,"uid":2054,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T04:24:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EjAaFA7U4AQR_T8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEjAaFA7U4AQR_T8.jpg&h=b43952d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea81980a0f2643e5c9f8937a0476569c0d79e469","tid":2388293,"uid":84102,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T04:24:54.000Z","msg":"好多基層4萬都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d04492bdf25e4263b777d5f2daae6d1819c98c4","tid":2388293,"uid":75390,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T04:25:09.000Z","msg":"邊有咁少<br />\n大把香港人有好多離岸戶口收埋仲多錢"},{"pid":"b8154c418bd0b209a5eb8c3e0efa036d8c13a24a","tid":2388293,"uid":196924,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"5d75c0daab160fee38f5e33f5d7ba6144138e0bc","tid":2388293,"uid":2054,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T04:24:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EjAaFA7U4AQR_T8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEjAaFA7U4AQR_T8.jpg&h=b43952d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T04:25:50.000Z","msg":"Mean 40k<br />\nMedian 19k<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19774c4cfc3bf65f7864b7700d6c713473a468f2","tid":2388293,"uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T04:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZNCVDs1.gif&amp;h=4ed5c0c3&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"6007460ee3b65152b60c4888dcb7a66f5f187d49","tid":2388293,"uid":42192,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T04:26:10.000Z","msg":"我同李嘉誠兩個人平均財富唔知幾撚多個億<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a942867db2620ee989e2b7543b744927656c8b","tid":2388293,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dis